GOAL: Enable file transaction to servers using file transfer protocol[FTP]

1. configure sftp in an instance such that, it can receive files via port number 22 to the specific directory as the specific user.ie, the sftp users have restricted privileges.
2. verify the working with any FTP client like filezilla, cyberduck etc.

3. install and configure vsftp in an instance such that, it can receive files very securely via port 21 to the configured directory as configures user.for Vsftp also privileges are restricted.
4. verify the working with any FTP client.
